<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idee33c6c8-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s473c"><num value="473c">§ 473c.</num><heading> Rules and regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of Agriculture is further authorized to make such rules and regulations as he may deem necessary to effectuate the purposes of this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idee33c6c9-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/act/1927-03-03/ch337/s3c">Mar. 3, 1927, ch. 337, § 3c</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/act/1937-04-13/ch75">Apr. 13, 1937, ch. 75</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/50/62">50 Stat. 62</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
